name: Not myself
description:
Hello there!

You know there are games that has
first or second person view
but have you ever tought about how 
does a second person view look alike?

Whit this project I've tryed to make one
of these second person view games. I hope I did it succesfully.

What do I have to do in this game?

  • you have to get 5 person to the hotel (wich is above the spawn point)
  • get rid of everyone else (lava or hotel)
  • escape from the island (with a boat)
  • escape with the queen

This game was made for the Miz Jam 1.

Artistic assets are from the Kenney 1-Bit Art Pack: https://kenney.nl/assets/bit-pack
